    "To avoid such complications, we will only consider correlation functions where the overall Y 0 charge vanishes in section 3.3.",
    "JHEP04(2024)048The action (2.3) is therefore manifestly supersymmetric in the target space, and can be thought of as a Green-Schwarz [39] treatment of the string.",
